          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/945.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the beef is browned, add your<strong> ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Add your <strong>honey</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until the beef becomes crispy, sticky and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> sticky chilli beef mince</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
